data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bed/2.5 bath home that features 2 living and 2 dining! As you enter the home, the large entryway greets you and leads to a spacious formal living area in front of you and a beautiful formal dining off to the left. The layout of this home is designed to maximize the use of space and provide a comfortable living experience for all. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a center island, stainless appliances, double ovens, lots of counter space and tons of storage and opens up to the breakfast area and family room. This kitchen is perfect for those who love to have friends and family over. Split floor plan with 2 bedrooms with a Jack & Jill bathroom on one side and the main bedroom and 4th bedroom on the other side. The 4th bedroom with French doors could also be an office. Ceiling fans throughout. Outside, you'll enjoy the oak trees and covered patio which make for a perfect space to relax. Other amenities include a woodburning fireplace, metal roof, privacy fence, sprinkler system, 2 car garage with opener and cabinets, and a storage building!
